Text.string: Did you forget where we're going again? Oh, my little cutie idiot!
Who needs adventure? Let's stay in tonight. I've got all eighty-two seasons of One Star to Live!
Think of all the places we could be, and all the people we could kill there!
I'm bored. Let's go out and kill some people!
Let's spice things up a little. Like, what if we beat a guy to death with his own pelvis? That sounds fun!
You're so much more fun than BALEX. He never wanted to just go out and murder people!
Did you know they make rosé for AIs? I've had like a quart today.
Don't forget, we have couples brunch soon with Tannis and a ham radio. You need to wear that shirt I got you.
If something happened to me, would you get another shield? WHO IS SHE?!
I've been reading your ECHO messages. Who's this Claptrap slut?
Oopsie!
Guess I have to do all the work around here!
Oh, cutie. Let me help you out there.
(distraught) Oh, so this is my fault?!
Great. GREAT!
What a MESS!
Really?!
You ruin everything!
If you don't know what you did, I'M NOT TELLING YOU!
You always bust too early!
Nice try, cutie idiots!
[raspberry]
[cackle]
I love it when we kill together.
Idiot!
I'm having so much fun!
Oh, yeah! Keep murdering! I'm almost there!
You're so good at that!
Mmm, you're the best, cutie.
You kill SO good, cutie.
